# #############################################################################
#
#   INVENTAR v0.1.0
#
#   KLASSEN (50):
#     Fassaden (7): Object, Agent, Lex, Structura, Possibile,
#                   Norma, Institutio
#     Object (1): Site
#     Data (10):  Data, Identifier, Result, ProductPassport,
#                 DigitalProductPassport,
#                 VerifiableCredential, VerifiablePresentation,
#                 Proof, CryptographicKey, BillOfMaterials
#     Agent (9):  Person (∩Object), Hardware (∩Object),
#                 Material (∩Object), Substance (∩Object),
#                 Specimen (∩Object),
#                 Software (∩Data), DigitalTwin (⊂Software),
#                 Organization (∩Institutio),
#                 EnvironmentAgent (∩Process)
#     Process (1): Process
#     Boundary (1): Boundary
#     Lex (1):      Law
#     Structura (1): Model
#     Possibile (1): Scenario
#     Norma (1):     Requirement
#     Institutio (9): Certification, Accreditation, Registry,
#                     TrustFramework, Regulation, Specification,
#                     LifecyclePhase, LegalEntity, Typus
#     Typus (6):     MaterialGrade, ProcessType, ProductType,
#                    DataFormat,
#                    BoundaryType, ModelType
#
#   ELIMINIERT (gegenüber Eingabe):
#     Product → Rolle via ProductType
#     ResultFile → Data + DataFormat
#     HardwareAgent → Hardware ist immer Agent
#     SoftwareAgent → Software ist immer Agent
#     hasFormat → typifiedBy DataFormat
#     HardwareType → ProductType
#     SoftwareType → ProductType
#
#   FASSADEN (52): 45 OP + 5 DP + 2 AP
#   EIGENE OP (30)
#   EIGENE DP (18)
#   DISJUNKTHEITSAXIOME (3): Agent, Institutio, Typus
#   MODELING PATTERNS (18)
#
# #############################################################################
